casebody.data:
ROCKWOOD CASUALTY INSURANCE COMPANY, Petitioner,
v.
DIRECTOR, OFFICE OF WORKERS' COMPENSATION PROGRAMS, DEPARTMENT OF LABOR, et al. No. 19-23. Supreme Court of the United States. March 30, 2020

Motion of respondent Tony Kourianos for attorney's fees and expenses granted. The Court approves the attorney's fees of $22,106.25 and expenses of $1,531.53.
